  \ </div>\n <div id=\"recipeRightColumn\">\n  <div id=\"recipeSteps\">\n   ## Steps:\n\
  \   <ol id=\"stepList\">\n    <li>\n     Make a variable to hold the player's score.\n\
  \     ```\n\nint score = 0;\n\n```\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ask the player a riddle.\n\
  \     [Here](http://brainden.com/logic-riddles.htm)\n     are some ideas.\n    </li>\n\
  \    <li>\n     If they get the answer right, pop up \"correct!\" and increase the\
  \ score by one\n     ```\n\nscore++;\n\n```\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Otherwise,\
